Wildrider stood up and heard all the chaos in the forest, "Well at least
they are finding things to do" he then noticed the Quintesson rumaging
around. "What are you doing here you disgusting organic" Wildrider said
accusingly as he pointed his gun at the quintesson.

The Quintesson changed heads with a whirling noise, and started to speak,
"I am here to simply offer my services, for the good of the Decepticons",
and this sentence was met with a loud and wild cackle from Wildrider, who
laughed uncontrolably, and scarily. "Sure you are, come with me" he said
then under his breath finished the sentence, "you little organic freak" as
he was followed into the ship by the Quintesson.
